data.description: South Anchorage 4 plex, the location is unbeatable for short and long term tenants! Low maintenance exterior and all units are up-to-date The owners unit is 3 bed/1bath, laundry in unit, comes with a 2 car garage and large deck above the garage. The other 3 units are 2 bed/ 1 bath with laundry in unit. Tenants pay gas, electric, and trash.
